SubString.CExoString: To the brave men and women who fought so bravely to hold this villiage against the Axfells, we thank you from the bottom of our souls. Forever rest in peace.

This is all that remains of the great Cleaven fort of Ramsallis. It was destroyed in a great battle against the Axfells. A massive Axfell army was gathering to attack the city, so Captain Prime evacuated the entire fort with the exception of a few dedicated warriors who stayed to hold off the Axfell invasion. The fort was destroyed that day, but a new one was soon built. This plaque stands in commemoration of the valiant warriors who gave their lives so that we may live today.
Place this object in any area where you want tracking to occur. Set Will to the DC of tracking in this area.
